newgameClicked

public void newgameClicked(double latitude,
                           double longitude)
This method opens a new GameActivity. The latitude and longitude are passed along to the next activity, to be placed into an SQLite Database.

Parameters:
latitude - the latitude of the location where the user wants to create a game
longitude - the longitude of the location where the user wants to create a game
